reviewText: This was part of a collection for our son.  The condition was acceptable, and was shipped in a timely fashion.  It is a great way to add to collections, without having to spend a lot of money.

Contains "Never Everglades" (from ep. 3), "To Kilimanjaro Bird" (from ep. 5) and "Rafiki Fables: Good Mousekeeping" (from ep. 2).

This is the first volume in the series. Highly recommend it for the die hard Disney and Lion Ling fans and collectors.
